#' Briefly, total RNA from whole blood, depleted of globin transcripts, was sequenced (2x50-bp) using the Illumina
#' HiSeq 2000 platform, and read alignment was performed using STAR (v2.5.3a).
#'
#' DNA methylation data and RNA-seq data were generated within the Biobank-based Integrative Omics Studies Consortium (http://wiki.bbmri.nl/wiki/BIOS_start-).
#' The data comprise six biobanks: Cohort on Diabetes and Atherosclerosis Maastricht (CODAM, n~180)
#' (doi: 10.1111/j.1365-2362.2010.02418.x), LifeLines (LL, n~700) (doi: 10.1136/bmjopen-2014-006772),
#' the Leiden Longevity Study (LLS, n~600) (doi: 10.1111/j.1532-5415.2009.02381.x),
#' the Rotterdam Study (RS, n~600) (doi: 10.1007/s10654-011-9610-5),
#' the Netherlands Twin Registry (NTR, n~1800) (doi:  10.1017/thg.2012.140) and
#' the Prospective ALS Study Netherlands (PAN, n~180) (doi: 10.1136/jnnp.2011.244939).
#' Sample identity of DNA methylation and gene expression data was confirmed using genotype data.
#'
#' Data were generated by the Human Genotyping facility (HugeF) of ErasmusMC, the Netherlands (www.glimDNA.org).
#'
#' @docType data
#' @name rnaSeqData_ReadCounts_BIOS_Freeze2_unrelated_GRCh38
#' @usage data(rnaSeqData_ReadCounts_BIOS_Freeze2_unrelated_GRCh38)
#'
#' @format An object of class \code{"SummarizedExperiment"}; see \code{\link[SummarizedExperiment]{SummarizedExperiment}}.
#'
#' @keywords datasets
#' @export
#' @examples
#' data(rnaSeqData_ReadCounts_BIOS_Freeze2_unrelated_GRCh38)
#' counts
rnaSeqData_ReadCounts_BIOS_Freeze2_unrelated_GRCh38 <- NULL

